 자주 생각해요.\n히나와 나란히 서기 위해서는 뭐가 필요할까, 하고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event156-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"Roselia의 기타리스트로서, 자신의 소리에 긍지를 갖고 있어요.\n그럼에도 불구하고 히나의 소리를 눈부시게 느끼고 말아요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event156-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"지금 제 소리에는 아직 무언가가 부족하다, 그런 느낌이 들어요.\n기술적인 부분뿐만 아니라, 경험도……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event156-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"유키나","body":"경험……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event156-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"Roselia와 Pastel＊Palettes의\n큰 차이는 뭐라고 생각하세요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFact